    "f5332588-ee9e-4cb8-b588-7497ef23f2f0": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "c1f503b4-5a46-4990-8e45-753347835b3c": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "About the role",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "template--18850231484751__f5332588-ee9e-4cb8-b588-7497ef23f2f0-16824067253affbd63-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You know what’s exploding too? Our ambition to become one of the most loved companies in the world. We want to be able to have our customers take our decisions for us. After all, we’re here to <strong>add the most value to their lives<\/strong> as possible. It’s a challenge, we know. That’s why we’re hiring a Customer Experience Manager. Someone who can: <\/p><h5>Build a global team<\/h5><p>We’re expanding fast, and we need a global Customer Experience team to support this growth. We empower our leaders to take ownership so you’ll have the possibility to <strong>shape the team<\/strong> based on your extensive experience.<\/p><h5>Fuel customer centricity<\/h5><p>A customer-centric company is aware of who their customers exactly are and what they want, and makes sure that the <strong>customer’s input<\/strong> is at the heart of all relevant decisions, big or small. Making the right customer insights accessible to the right teams, and having them implement them in order to improve the <strong>customer experience<\/strong>, is what drives a customer centric company. At Loop we have set the foundation for this with e.g. a feedback loop, and a monthly internal newsletter with customer insights. Now it’s up to you to build on this and bring Loop to the next level of customer centricity.<\/p><h5>Improve our Net Promoter Score<\/h5><p>We firmly believe that putting our customer first in everything we do, will set us apart and drive our ambition to <strong>become a love brand<\/strong>. Our ambition is to shoot for the stars. Meaning our<strong> NPS<\/strong> should be in the upper range and among the absolute best in industry. If not the very best. Think of <strong>Tesla and Apple<\/strong>. Well, we want to go above and beyond that, one day. Your role is to guide Loop towards this ambitious goal.<br\/> <br\/><strong>Your end-goal?<\/strong> To install the Customer Experience team as one of the most foundational teams at Loop, <strong>knowing our customers inside-out <\/strong>and providing all teams with relevant insights that they can use in order to improve their work. But no need to limit yourself to that role though. Found a way to improve our <strong>customer retention rate<\/strong> or improve upon our loyalty system? Let’s hear it. We’re a scale-up, we’re all about failing fast and cheap to win big together. <strong>Just pitch it to us<\/strong>. <\/p>",
            "description_padding": 32
          }
        },
        "82ff3a37-8cad-430f-95db-9cbdeeef6ec9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What you’ll do",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "32a98dbe-f634-469b-8904-0f5d2149e699": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>Manage and grow a global team of <strong>5+ Customer Experience Specialists<\/strong><\/li><li>Build and install <strong>customer-centricity foundations<\/strong> cross-departmental throughout a fast-paced global scaleup<\/li><li>Improve upon Loop’s <strong>customer-centric culture<\/strong><\/li><li>Fight to remove all pain points and introduce <strong>moments of delight <\/strong>throughout the entire customer journey <\/li><li>Implement, analyze and improve upon metrics across the customer journey e.g. <strong>NPS <\/strong><\/li><li>Support teams Customer Happiness, CRM & MA and Community<\/li><li>Introduce ways to know the customer deeply at any given moment  <\/li><li>Become the <strong>voice of the customer <\/strong>across all departments  <\/li><li>Innovate across the broader Loop marketing arm to <strong>drive cross functional initiatives<\/strong> that improve DTC experience <\/li><\/ul>",
            "description_padding": 32
          }
        },
        "d99470d8-e10d-499d-af5b-a48e327e428f": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How you'll do it",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "82e61271-9c1d-4bd4-aee8-3f6ae305e621": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li><strong>10+ year experience<\/strong> in Customer Experience roles in ecommerce<\/li><li>Ambitious manager passionate about <strong>growing teams<\/strong> and working with people<\/li><li>A <strong>charismatic<\/strong> people person that has the power the make a cultural impact<\/li><li><strong>Passionate<\/strong> about customer-centricity, getting to know the customers deeply and wanting to provide the best possible solutions for them <\/li><li>Proven marketer who understands and has worked in a <strong>DTC digital marketing<\/strong> environment<\/li><li><strong>Entrepreneurial mindset <\/strong>will come in handy, but that’s true for all things in life <\/li><li>The ability to <strong>glean clear, salient ideas from complex information <\/strong>and very clearly communicate them to a diverse set of stakeholders in a way they will understand<\/li><li>A highly organized \"doer\" with an exceptional ability to <strong>multitask<\/strong>, who will take initiative and execute.<\/li><li>You’re in our <strong>Antwerp<\/strong> office from time to time, but otherwise you’re free to work wherever. Why? You need to work with a lot of different teams within the company. And that’s just easier in person.<\/li><\/ul>",
            "description_padding": 32
          }
        },
